- GEM-IMG,XIMG   GEM and Ventura Publisher up to 24Bps, Atari ST.
- MSP         MS-Paint, Windows 2.0.
- MAC         Macintosh-Paint.
- PIC         Macintosh PICT in 1,2,4,8,24 BPS.
