- SCR         Word capture
- CDR,CCH     Corel draw Icon
- SKD         Autosketch Icon
- RAW
- PNM         UNIX Portable Bitmap 1,8,24 Bps (Jef Poskanzer).
- ACB,BBM     IFF Brushes and ACBM Files.
- DAT         Framegrabber Video 1000/2000  Fricke/Berlin.
- FRM         Echolab
